    "40, 290.41, 331.0, 331.11, 331.19, 331.82, G30.0, G30.1, G30.8, G30.9, G31.01, G31.09, G31.83, F01.50, and F01.51 (for ADRD).",
    "To enhance the representation of nodes and relations in the KG, we perform preprocessing before integrating SuppKG and SemMedDB for filtering out generic, uninformative and incorrect triples.",
